## `safira-cli insomnia test`

Run your insomnia test

```
USAGE
  $ safira-cli insomnia test [-h] [--inso-spec-name <value>]

FLAGS
  -h, --help                Show CLI help.
  --inso-spec-name=<value>  The name of the INSO specification.

DESCRIPTION
  Run your insomnia test
```
